<br />

<br />
For those who play on test, can you see if this only applies to summoned pets, or does it affect charmed pets as well? If charmed pets are affected then we will no longer be able to use clicky invis to break charm.
<br />

<br />
I for one will be very disappointed if I can no longer use my mosquito boots to break charm.</span></td>
