				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Pets no longer poof when owner is invis (on test)<a name="65018"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 30 04 6:10 AM</span></td>
